text: Subonnet Sue is a 1945 American musical comedy movie directed by Ralph Murphy and starring Gale Storm, Phil Regan, George Cleveland, Minna Gombell, Edna Holland, Raymond Hatton, Alan Mowbray. It was distributed by Monogram Pictures and was nominated for an Academy Award in 1946. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1945 comedy movies Category:1945 musical movies Category:American musical comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Ralph Murphy
title: Sunbonnet Sue
